%section#wv-sundays
  .shadow
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-12
        %h1 sundays - what to expect
        %p You are really welcome to join us on a Sunday morning whether you are a church regular or have never been before. Our service starts at 10.30am and finishes at 12 noon. Free refreshments are served for 20 minutes beforehand - come and grab a coffee. Most of us come dressed casually, but if you want to wear a brand new suit, that's fine!

        %p
          We meet at the
          %a{:href => '#wv-find-us'} Vineyard Centre.
          We have a fully accessible venue with free parking including Blue Badge holder spaces.
    .row
      .col-md-4
        %h3 we start with worship
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/sunday/worship.jpg'}
        %p A live band leads us in about 25 minutes of heartfelt sung worship. The words are on the screen and you can join in or just sit back and listen.
      .col-md-4
        %h3 learn together
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/sunday/insight.jpg'}
        %p
          We have a talk based on the Bible and our experience of Jesus. It's not just theory; the talks are relevant to our day to day lives and there are always things to put into practice.
        %p
          %a{:href => '#wv-talks'} Listen to recordings of past talks &raquo;
      .col-md-4
        %h3 and make a response
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/sunday/response.jpg'}
        %p At the end of the talk we reflect on what we have heard and respond. There is the opportunity to choose to follow Jesus at this time, or the chance to receive prayer. There is no pressure to participate, but always the chance to respond if you wish.
    .row
      .col-sm-4
        %h3 kids church
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/sunday/kids-church.jpg'}
        %p Church isn't just for grown ups! We run age-appropriate interactive groups for 0-11s so they can learn about Jesus in a safe and fun environment. Our volunteer welcome team at the door can help your family settle in the right places. You can sign your children into their groups from 10.20am.
      .col-sm-4
        %h3 youth
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/sunday/youth.jpg'}

        %p Our youth (11-18s) meet during the service in the Youth Café. We play games and eat chocolate, whilst learning what it means to follow Jesus as a teenager today.

        %p Our kids and youth team have up to date DBS checks.

      .col-sm-4
        %h3 finding out more
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/sunday/coffee.jpg'}
        %p The service ends about midday. If it's your first visit we'd love to meet you! You can join some of our staff team in the connect area at the back of the café to have a coffee and ask any questions.

