        %h1 a living community
        %p We have many places for you to get involved, connect, and belong, no matter what your age or life stage.
        %h2 life groups
        %p Our Life Groups are at the heart of our church. They meet in peoples homes in Winchester and the surrounding areas. They are made up of 6-15 people and are a great place to get to know others, share both the important and the insignificant things of life and learn to do the things Jesus did.
        %h2 how to join a group
        %p
          Most groups meet weekly. You are welcome to try a few to find the one where you feel most at home. Browse the map below and
